        "content": "<p>Repeating my comment from the PR, this instance also works:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">instance</span> <span class=\"n\">function.module</span>\n  <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"n\">Î²</span> <span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Type</span><span class=\"bp\">*</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">semiring</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">add_comm_monoid</span> <span class=\"n\">Î²</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"n\">Î²</span><span class=\"o\">]</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">module</span> <span class=\"n\">R</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">X</span> <span class=\"bp\">â†’</span> <span class=\"n\">Î²</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"n\">apply_instance</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
